47
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.130
And I just want a million dollars!
而我只想要一百万美金

48
00:00:04.260 --> 00:00:05.340
Rachel?
瑞秋

49
00:00:05.510 --> 00:00:08.220
Oh, God, Monica! Hi! Thank God!
噢 老天爷 摩妮卡 感谢上帝

50
00:00:08.390 --> 00:00:11.560
I went to your building and this guy with a hammer said...
我刚到你那里去 而你不在 那个拿着大锤子的家伙说...

51
00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:13.930
...that you might be here, and you are.
你可能在这里 你真在这里

52
00:00:14.190 --> 00:00:17.690
- Can I get you some coffee?  - Decaf.
- 你想喝点咖啡吗？- 无咖啡因的

53
00:00:18.270 --> 00:00:22.230
Okay, everybody, this is Rachel, another Lincoln High survivor.
好了 各位 这位是瑞秋 另一个林肯高中的幸存者

54
00:00:22.490 --> 00:00:24.950
This is everybody. This is Chandler and Phoebe...
这就是各位 这是钱德  菲比

55
00:00:25.150 --> 00:00:27.410
...and Joey. And remember my brother, Ross?
乔伊  还有 你还记得我哥哥罗斯吗？

56
00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:28.700
- Sure!  - Hey.
- 当然  - 嘿

57
00:00:28.870 --> 00:00:30.780
- Hi.  - Oh, God.
- 嗨  - 天啊

58
00:00:38.580 --> 00:00:39.860
So you wanna tell us now,
那你现在可以告诉我们了吗？

59
00:00:39.860 --> 00:00:42.570
or are we waiting for four wet bridesmaids?
还是说我们在等着四位湿漉的伴娘？

60
00:00:44.420 --> 00:00:49.390
Oh, God! Well, it started about a half-hour before the wedding.
好吧 大概在婚礼前半个小时

61
00:00:49.550 --> 00:00:51.970
I was in this room with all the presents...
我在礼物间里

62
00:00:52.140 --> 00:00:53.970
...and I was looking at this gravy boat.
看着那个肉汁壶

63
00:00:54.180 --> 00:00:57.600
This really gorgeous Limoges gravy boat.
那是个非常好看的肉汁壶

64
00:00:57.770 --> 00:00:59.600
When all of a sudden... Sweet 'N Low?
然后 突然…有代糖吗？

65
00:00:59.770 --> 00:01:01.900
I realized...
我发现…

66
00:01:02.070 --> 00:01:05.990
...I was more turned on by this gravy boat than by Barry.
我对这个肉汁壶 比对巴瑞更有冲动

67
00:01:06.150 --> 00:01:09.200
Then I got really freaked out, and that's when it hit me:
然后我吓呆了 然后这个想法突然出现在脑中:

68
00:01:09.370 --> 00:01:12.160
How much Barry looks like Mr. Potato Head.
巴瑞看起来多像洋芋头先生啊

69
00:01:12.580 --> 00:01:15.830
You know, I mean, I always knew he looked familiar, but...
我总是觉得他眼熟 但是…

70
00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:21.340
Anyway, I just had to get out of there, and I started wondering:
总之 我必须离开那里 我在想:

71
00:01:21.590 --> 00:01:25.170
"Why am I doing this?" And "Who am I doing this for?"
"我为什么这样做？我为谁这样做？"

72
00:01:25.340 --> 00:01:29.720
Anyway, I just didn't know where to go, and I know you and I have drifted apart...
我不知道该去哪里 而且我知道我和你有点疏远了

73
00:01:29.930 --> 00:01:32.760
...but you're the only person I know in the city.
但你是我这个城市里唯一认识的人

74
00:01:32.970 --> 00:01:34.640
Who wasn't invited to the wedding.
而且没有受邀参加你的婚礼

75
00:01:35.020 --> 00:01:37.930
Oh, I was kind of hoping that wouldn't be an issue.
噢 我希望你不会把它当一回事…